commit.message:
Only keep farthest failures

This avoids construction of unnecessary failure objects.

Massage function names when throwing errors

In particular, strip off an initial underscore, replace all other
underscores by spaces. Turns '_new_line' to 'new line'.

Only store test in the ParsingError

Don't store it in every failure object.
Add more coverage, support hidden decorator.
Raise only ParseError, add nice message.
Remove custom position support for now, integrate it more.
Move position tracking off the parser.
Add Parser.consume that returns range info.

Merge pull request #2 from avakar/tests
